dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Arthur Hall. May I have your name, please?
Hi Arthur, my name is Cheryl Parker.
Nice to meet you, Cheryl. How can I assist you today?
I'd like to file a new claim for an incident that occurred last week.
Of course, Cheryl. Can you please provide me with the date and time of the incident?
The incident happened on five seven two zero at nine zero zero in the morning.
Thank you, Cheryl. Could you also provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
My policy number is four eight six two one zero.
Thank you for the information, Cheryl. I will start working on your claim. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Cheryl. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
